Activate or Deactivate Sensitive Data Rules from the Rules List View

This change applies to enhanced Messaging channels, Messaging for In-App and Web, and Voice. 

In Setup, go to the Sensitive Data Rules for Enhanced Channels page. 
Click any ruleâ€™s action menu and select Activate or Deactivate. 
You can have up to 10 active sensitive data rules at a time for enhanced channels. If you reach this limit, create additional rules but can't activate them without first deactivating others.
title: Activate or Deactivate Sensitive Data Rules in Service Cloud
